cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.NI, cs.DB, cs.LG. 

The paper discusses security and privacy challenges in the Internet of Things (IoT) and proposes the use of blockchain to enhance security. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves machine learning algorithms and data analysis, which suggests the possibility of cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of blockchain and IoT devices also implies the relevance of cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.DB (Databases).
